==Information==
===American Destroyer Escort Release===
*The American Destroyer Escort (Samuel B. Roberts (?)) will be implemented on April 23rd, on the KanColle 5th Anniversary Date. 
**She will be illustrated by a New Artist joining KanColle for the first time.
===Fletcher-class Destroyer Coming Soon===
*A Fletcher-class Destroyer is planned for release soon.
===Kagerou & Yuugumo-class Destroyers 2nd Remodel===
*The Upcoming Kai Ni Remodels in the near future will be focused on the Kagerou and Yuugumo-class.
**It is currently planned to have at least 3 Kagerou-class Destroyers to receive Kai Ni Remodels by the Summer.
***The Kagerou-class Destroyers 1st Ship: {{ShipLink|Kagerou}} will be receiving it first.
===KanColle Phase 2 & HTML5 Transition===
*Before the Transition into HTML5, a Lottery will be held this Spring, where the winning Admirals will be elligible to move to another Server.
*The Game Display Screen will be expanded via the HTML5 Transition.
*The Full Completion of the transition into KanColle Phase 2 is expected to take 1 Year. 

